sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant A as 🤖 AI Agent<br/>(Claude Code)
    participant M as MCP Server<br/>(auditor-mcp)
    participant B as Auditor Backend<br/>(Express.js)
    participant S as Stellar Testnet<br/>(USDC SAC)
    participant R as RAG Engine<br/>(local embeddings)
    participant G as Groq<br/>(AI Engine)

    A->>M: audit_soroban_contract_mpp(file_path)
    M->>M: readFile(file_path)

    M->>B: mppClient.fetch()<br/>POST /api/audit/mpp<br/>{ code: "..." }
    B-->>M: HTTP 402<br/>MPP challenge<br/>HMAC-signed ID · 0.15 USDC<br/>USDC SAC · stellar:testnet

    Note over M,S: Agent pays autonomously — no human approval

    M->>S: SAC transfer 0.15 USDC<br/>stellar.charge() · Stellar keypair
    S-->>M: Transaction hash + receipt

    M->>B: POST /api/audit/mpp (retry)<br/>X-MPP-Credential: payment proof
    B->>S: mppx verifies SAC receipt on-chain
    S-->>B: Verified ✓

    B->>R: embed contract code<br/>cosine similarity search
    R-->>B: top-4 relevant security doc chunks<br/>(Sanctifier · OpenZeppelin · CWE)

    B->>G: Pass 1 — chain-of-thought reasoning<br/>(auth, arithmetic, storage, events)<br/>+ RAG context injected
    G-->>B: Reasoning trace

    B->>G: Pass 2 — structured JSON extraction
    G-->>B: findings[] with CWE IDs + severity

    B-->>M: HTTP 200<br/>{ findings: [...], model, summary, reasoning }
    M-->>A: Structured audit report
